A lone figure in a protective hazmat suit standing at the edge of a vast server farm at dusk, wielding a glowing electric staff while facing a horde of shadowy, translucent computer monitors with cracked screens shuffling toward them like undead creatures. The monitors emit an eerie green phosphorescent glow from their broken displays. The scene is rendered in cyberpunk style with neon purple and toxic green color palette, rain-slicked ground reflecting the lights, massive data center towers looming in the misty background with blinking red warning lights. The atmosphere is tense and apocalyptic, mixing digital decay with physical deterioration, cables snaking across the ground like tentacles.
